name: Performance optimization release using pyexcel-io 0.1.0
body: This release is backward compatible with earlier releases. 'streaming' is an extra option given to get_data. Only when 'streaming' is explicitly set to True, the data will be consisted of generators, hence will break your existing code.

name: Enforce reading values if a cell contains a formular
body: Openpyxl had a data_only option upon opening a xlsx file. By passing data_only=True, this library would be able to read values back.
